Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,♪〜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.08,0:01:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,〜♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.51,0:01:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell if we're in a draking vessel\Nor riding a wild horse...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.77,0:01:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we don't bump into anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's if we don't end up\Nin pieces first...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You think Takita will be able\Nto reach this hell of a place?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have any other place to search,\Nwe can only hope she's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.99,0:01:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We're reaching our limit here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.09,0:02:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We know already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention, crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The 48 hours of emergency search\Nhave come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it pains our heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,all activities regarding the search\Nare suspended as of now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.41,0:02:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't savour that dragon yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-saan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Bridge! Starboard and straight away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.69,0:03:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,At those pointy rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Capella!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Going full starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this for real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind has carried her voice here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.96,0:03:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot remain static\Nwith this wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Move our right horizontal tail\Nas closer to the rocks as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Vanabelle! Support the bridge\Nin my place!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The altitude is fine,\N10 degrees to our right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Miikaaa-saaan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Miiiikaaa-saaaan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Miiikaaa-saaan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Miiikaaa-saaan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita!! Jump!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita... You were alive as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Luck's about the only thing\NI have going for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.79,0:04:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ascella-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very, very much\Nfor taking care of me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forget you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,for as long as I live!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're that lucky, I'm sure\Nwe will meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So that was the famous "Mika-san"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a draker, don't fall\Noff like that ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, that little thing\Non your back...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the cub of the dragon that\Nfell with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't tasted a dragon cub\Nin my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wai-!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wipe off your drool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wai- The wind's spreading it\Nat my fac-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.59,0:05:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ew! So dirty...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Mika-san...! Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Vannie-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I worried you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank god.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that this is the place\Nthat "ferry" was aiming for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Vannie-san, Mika-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,can I count on you to help me\Nwithout asking any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm returning this little one\Nto the pod!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... the real Takita?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I smell bad! I'm aware of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.90,0:06:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So... you're the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, I'm sorry I worried you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Takita!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It- It's her voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you even know how many\Nproblems have you caused to us all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita! I'm glad you were safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:07:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I believed she was alright\Nfrom the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Any wounds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,As serious as ever, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let it slide this one time, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I am... completely fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad she's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope she isn't a ghost...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is one hell of a girl alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This has been harder than\Nchasing dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad she's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.55,0:07:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I didn't specially...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind has calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh! They're gonna leaving this\None behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:07:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a different dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! They're gonna hunt down\Nthat pod!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.16,0:08:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.41,0:08:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragons preying on each other!\NWhat a rare sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.37,0:08:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell everyone to follow\Nthat dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do that, we will get closer\Nto that pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocco-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a different type of dragon\Nthat has appeared to hunt down that pod!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That type...! It's a real rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they'd sell well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? You mean to hunt them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We came here to do that\Nin the first place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard it already! Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.61,0:08:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard the bridge, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita has come back and she brought\Nextra dragons with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We sure can't get bored with\Nher around us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're damn right! What a\Nspunky girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dead tired though...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving the emotional reunion\Nfor after this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,One last work before the celebration!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring all your strenght and let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to raise our altitude even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Engine room, how's things?\NCan we bear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been forcing it pretty\Nbad already...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides that, you should be worrying\Nabout the hull more than the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh? As long as we don't bump into\Nanything we'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocco-san! Don't speak as if this\Nhasn't anything to do with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We're running out of oxygen\Nand the engine is knocking nonstop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.07,0:09:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we should change the fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiro, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... she's treating us like slaves...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're entering the clouds!\NAll hands on deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be on port side!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll be on starboard then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We have poor visibility,\Nbe careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.17,0:09:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita, you're hurt, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be wandering around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were to fall again, then what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:09:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Go inside and rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.48,0:10:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragons... attacking other dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Gibbs...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Those dragons are focused on the pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.53,0:10:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment they have their jaws\Nbusy, shoot them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.51,0:10:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Uwah! What's with this number?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they coming from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem like moths\Ngathering at a light.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the so called\Ndragon corridor...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot believe my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If something like this exists...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to fly around the\Nworld searching for them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But a dragon corridor is\Na very strange phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only see one every few years\Nand they always appear suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't predict something like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.83,0:11:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Soraya, I think you should study\Neven if it's only a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When the smoke blows,\Ndragons will pass by...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,With this situation, I can't even\Nthink of a way to return this little one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He- hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're alone, you and I, eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up with that anchor!\NKeep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're finished here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Let's hurry up and go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, over there... something is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:12:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Tha- that's stupidly big...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen one like that in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The group that is anchoring, hurry up\Nand get them back in the ship now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.22,0:12:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Full starboard, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.95,0:12:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Jaw dropping...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.91,0:12:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it saw this feast going on and\Ncame down from the upper layers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,0:12:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take on the elevator!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We're retreating away from this place, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.67,0:12:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a strong wind blowing towards north!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go around and\Nride the airflow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming at us...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's riding the same wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a huge dragon that\Nnone of us have seen before!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:12:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna hunt it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Mika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone on the ship yet?\NWe're retreating!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Takita.\N-Vannie-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a draker too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your duty as one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And what will you do, Vannie-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave that idiot alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... what the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What a day...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.82,0:13:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiro-san, I've been looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the autogyro able to fly now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying all of a sudden...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But... you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to return this little one\Nno matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll prepare the high altitude fuel for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But, whatever happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, what are you doing?\NIt's dangerous out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.57,0:14:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm launching you for real!\NAre you really sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I see a lot of problems with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Damnit... Why are you always\Ncausing issues, Takita?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This fuel sometimes gets air into the motor\Nso it can be a bit difficult to accelerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Ah... okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare... fall off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ye-...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.02,0:14:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't shake it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:15:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... let's get back to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen... what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.49,0:15:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! What the hell are they doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Jiro-san! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Damnit... Why am I doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Vanabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing,\Ngoddamnit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hunting it, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.81,0:15:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it'll be so tasty...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita, why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.63,0:16:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm... I'm a draker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed this little one's mother\Nand ate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.59,0:16:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a draker, of course you'd do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.22,0:16:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.23,0:16:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We're... a dragon and a draker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I have to return\Nthis little one to its pod...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,so it can become a full-fledged dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Full-fledged?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.08,0:16:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I also want to live in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I think... I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You... you said to charge it with\Nextra power after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We kinda overdid it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But that explosion was the best, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Niko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,By a hair's breadth...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, my debt is settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.88,0:17:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita! Go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time we see each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm definetely going to hunt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm a draker after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why... till then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let anyone eat you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:17:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,'Sup.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita! Jiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.11,0:19:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell were you thinking\Nto do this now of all times?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiro, you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And you too, Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.83,0:19:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-Worrying all of us...\N-In the end
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-Think about what you're doing for once!\N-I missed the last shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The sunrise...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We can barely see the pod now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky is so big and wide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem alright!\NYou must be hungry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:20:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up inside, I'm gonna prep\Nbreakfast soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.41,0:20:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,One steak for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When you pull an all nighter,\Nno one cares about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the same goes for booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita's back and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta celebrate!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've taken a bite off of that\None when I got the chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh at me! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.06,0:20:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.19,0:20:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Chasing dragons that swim through the sky,\NTo the west, east, south and north.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Catching the wind, seizing the shadows,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,our journey goes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takita! Bring the explosives!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita, what are you doing?\NBring here the bomb lances!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.46,0:20:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks delicious... Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takita! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.73,0:21:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♪〜
